🧾 Step 3：完整 PowerShell 腳本（直接存成 fifo.ps1）
👉 這份是可直接跑版本（已幫你整理乾淨）
Import-Module ImportExcel

# ===== 輸入輸出 =====
$inputFile = "input.xlsx"
$outputFile = "output.xlsx"

# ===== 讀 Excel =====
$data = Import-Excel $inputFile

# ===== 欄位修正 =====
foreach ($row in $data) {
    if ($row.列標號) {
        $row.月份 = $row.列標號
    }
}

# ===== 找 _ 開頭欄位 =====
$columns = $data[0].PSObject.Properties.Name | Where-Object { $_ -like "_*" }

$allResults = @()

# ===== FIFO function =====
function Allocate($data, $col) {

    $demand = @()
    $supply = @()

    foreach ($r in $data) {

        $val = [double]$r.$col

        if ($val -gt 0) {
            $demand += ,@($r.月份, $val)
        }
        elseif ($val -lt 0) {
            $supply += ,@($r.月份, [math]::Abs($val))
        }
    }

    $result = @()

    $i = 0
    $j = 0

    while ($i -lt $demand.Count -and $j -lt $supply.Count) {

        $d_month = $demand[$i][0]
        $d_val   = $demand[$i][1]

        $s_month = $supply[$j][0]
        $s_val   = $supply[$j][1]

        $alloc = [math]::Min($d_val, $s_val)

        $result += [pscustomobject]@{
            '需求月份' = $d_month
            '供給月份' = $s_month
            '分配量'   = $alloc
            '欄位'     = $col
        }

        $demand[$i][1] -= $alloc
        $supply[$j][1] -= $alloc

        if ($demand[$i][1] -eq 0) { $i++ }
        if ($supply[$j][1] -eq 0) { $j++ }
    }

    return $result
}

# ===== 主迴圈 =====
foreach ($col in $columns) {

    Write-Host "處理中: $col"

    $res = Allocate $data $col
    $allResults += $res
}

# ===== 明細輸出 =====
$allResults | Export-Excel $outputFile -WorksheetName "明細" -AutoSize

# ===== 總結 =====
$summary = $allResults |
    Group-Object 欄位 |
    Select-Object @{Name="欄位";Expression={$_.Name}},
                  @{Name="總分配量";Expression={($_.Group | Measure-Object 分配量 -Sum).Sum}}

$summary | Export-Excel $outputFile -WorksheetName "總結" -AutoSize -Append

Write-Host "完成！輸出：$outputFile"

